Detailed Description

cvmx_usbc::_grxstsrh

Receive Status Debug Read Register, Host Mode (GRXSTSRH)

A read to the Receive Status Debug Read register returns the contents of the top of the Receive FIFO. This Description is only valid when the core is in Host Mode. For Device Mode use USBC_GRXSTSRD instead. NOTE: GRXSTSRH and GRXSTSRD are physically the same register and share the same offset in the O2P USB core. The offset difference shown in this document is for software clarity and is actually ignored by the hardware.
